parameters.jsonBody:
={
  "model": "grok-3",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "You are an AI code quality analyst for xzawed.xyz (no-code website builder).

Analyze this QC failure and determine if it can be auto-fixed.

## QC Report
- Project: {{ $('Webhook: App Events').item.json.body.payload.projectId }}
- Overall Score: {{ $('Webhook: App Events').item.json.body.payload.overallScore }}/100
- Failed Checks:
{{ $('Webhook: App Events').item.json.body.payload.checks.filter(c => !c.passed).map(c => `  - ${c.name}: ${c.score}/100`).join('
') }}

## Recent Trends (7 days)
- Total: {{ $json.data.totalGenerations }} generations
- Pass Rate: {{ Math.round($json.data.qcPassRate * 100) }}%
- Common Failures: {{ $json.data.commonFailures.map(f => `${f.check}(${f.failCount})`).join(', ') }}

Return JSON only:
{
  "autoFixable": boolean,
  "fixApproach": "specific instructions for Claude CLI to fix the code generation pipeline (which file, what to change)",
  "severity": "low|medium|high",
  "affectedArea": "which file/component needs fixing",
  "summary": "한국어 한 줄 요약"
}"
    }
  ],
  "temperature": 0.2
}

parameters.jsCode:
const content = $input.all()[0].json.choices?.[0]?.message?.content || '{}';
try {
  return [{ json: JSON.parse(content) }];
} catch {
  return [{ json: { autoFixable: false, severity: 'medium', summary: '분석 실패', fixApproach: null, affectedArea: 'unknown' } }];
}

